\c 28
\s Ukubusa kukaAhazi
\p
\v 1 UAhazi wayeleminyaka engamatshumi amabili esiba yinkosi; wabusa iminyaka elitshumi lesithupha eJerusalema. Kodwa kenzanga okuqondileyo emehlweni eN\nd kosi\nd*, njengoDavida uyise\x + 2 Kho. 16.2-4.\x*.
\v 2 Ngoba wahamba ezindleleni zamakhosi akoIsrayeli, wasesenzela oBhali\x + Hlu. 2.11.\x* izithombe ezibunjwe ngokuncibilikisa\x + Eks. 34.17.\x*.
\v 3 Yena watshisa impepha esihotsheni sendodana kaHinomu\x + Josh. 18.16.\x*, watshisa lamadodana akhe emlilweni, njengokwamanyala ezizwe iN\nd kosi\nd* eyazixotsha elifeni phambi kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli\x + 2 Kho. 16.5,6.\x*.
\v 4 Wanikela imihlatshelo watshisa impepha endaweni eziphakemeyo laphezu kwamaqaqa langaphansi kwaso sonke isihlahla esiluhlaza.
\v 5 Ngakho iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakhe yamnikela esandleni senkosi yeSiriya; asemtshaya, athumba kuye abathunjiweyo abanengi, abasa eDamaseko\x + 2 Kho. 16.5,6.\x*. Futhi wanikelwa esandleni senkosi yakoIsrayeli eyamtshaya ngokutshaya okukhulu.
\p
\v 6 Ngoba uPheka indodana kaRemaliya\x + 2 Kho. 15.27. 16.5.\x* wabulala koJuda abazinkulungwane ezilikhulu lamatshumi amabili ngasuku lunye, bonke bengamadoda alamandla, ngoba babeyidelile iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu waboyise.
\v 7 UZikiri iqhawe lakoEfrayimi wasebulala uMahaseya indodana yenkosi\x + 18.25. 1 Kho. 22.26.\x* loAzirikamu umphathi wendlu loElkana owesibili enkosini\x + 18.25. 1 Kho. 22.26.\x*.
\v 8 Abantwana bakoIsrayeli basebethumba kubafowabo abazinkulungwane ezingamakhulu amabili, abesifazana, amadodana, lamadodakazi; baphanga lempango enengi kibo, bayiletha impango eSamariya\x + 11.4. 28.11.\x*.
\v 9 Kodwa kwakukhona lapho umprofethi weN\nd kosi\nd* obizo lakhe lalinguOdedi; wasephuma phambi kwebutho elalisiza eSamariya, wathi kibo: Khangelani, ngenxa yolaka lweN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu waboyihlo phezu kukaJuda\x + Isa. 47.6. Hez. 25.12,15. 26.2. Obad. 10.\x*, ibanikele esandleni senu; libabulele-ke ngolaka olufinyelele emazulwini\x + Ezra 9.6. Isam. 18.5.\x*.
\v 10 Khathesi-ke lina lithi lehlisela ngaphansi kwenu abantwana bakoJuda labeJerusalema babe yizigqili lezigqilikazi. Kodwa lina kakulamacala yini kini amelene leN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu?
\v 11 Ngakho-ke ngilalelani; libuyisele abathunjiweyo elibathumbe kubafowenu, ngoba ukuvutha kolaka lweN\nd kosi\nd* kuphezu kwenu.
\v 12 Kwasekusukuma amadoda kunhloko zabantwana bakoEfrayimi, oAzariya indodana kaJohanani, uBerekiya indodana kaMeshilemothi, loJehizikiya\x + 28.27.\x* indodana kaShaluma\x + 2 Kho. 15.10.\x*, loAmasa indodana kaHadilayi, bamelana lalabo ababengena bevela ebuthweni.
\v 13 Basebesithi kibo: Kaliyikungenisa abathunjiweyo lapha kube licala eN\nd kosi\nd*ni limelene lathi; ngoba lina lithi lizakwengeza ezonweni zethu lemacaleni ethu, ngoba isiphambeko sethu sikhulu, lokuvutha kolaka kuphezu kukaIsrayeli.
\v 14 Ngakho abahlomileyo batshiya abathunjiweyo lempango phambi kweziphathamandla lebandla lonke\x + 20.21. 1 Lan. 12.23.\x*.
\v 15 Lamadoda abizwa ngamabizo asukuma, abamba abathunjiweyo\x + 28.12. 31.19. Nani 1.17.\x*, agqokisa bonke ababenqunu babo ngokuvela empangweni; yebo abagqokisa, abafaka amanyathela, abanika ukudla, abanathisa\x + 2 Kho. 6.22. Zaga 25.21,22. Roma 12.20.\x*, abagcoba, athwala bonke ababuthakathaka ngabobabhemi\x + Dute. 28.40. Ruthe 3.3. 2 Sam. 14.2. Mika 6.15.\x*, abasa eJeriko, umuzi wamalala, duze labafowabo; basebebuyela eSamariya\x + Dute. 34.3.\x*.
\p
\v 16 Ngalesosikhathi inkosi uAhazi yathuma emakhosini eAsiriya ukumncedisa.
\v 17 Ngoba amaEdoma ayesebuye atshaya uJuda, athumba abathunjwa\x + 2 Kho. 16.7.\x*.
\v 18 LamaFilisti\x + Hez. 16.27,57.\x* ayehlasele imizi\x + 25.13.\x* yesihotsha\x + 26.10. Josh. 15.33.\x* leningizimu yakoJuda, athumba iBeti-Shemeshi\x + Josh. 15.10.\x*, leAjaloni\x + Josh. 10.12.\x*, leGederothi\x + Josh. 15.41.\x*, leSoko\x + Josh. 15.35.\x* lemizana yayo\x + Nani 21.25.\x*, leTimina\x + Josh. 15.10.\x* lemizana yayo\x + Nani 21.25.\x*, leGimizo lemizana yayo\x + Nani 21.25.\x*; ahlala khona.
\v 19 Ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* yamthobisa uJuda ngenxa kaAhazi inkosi yakoIsrayeli\x + 21.2.\x*, ngoba wamenza ze uJuda, wasephambuka kakhulu eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + Eks. 32.25.\x*.
\v 20 Ngakho uTiligathi-Pileseri inkosi yeAsiriya\x + 2 Kho. 16.7.\x* wafika kuye, wamhlupha, kodwa kamqinisanga.
\v 21 Ngoba uAhazi wathatha isabelo sendlu kaJehova lesendlu yenkosi leseziphathamandla, wasipha inkosi yeAsiriya; kodwa kayimsizanga\x + 2 Kho. 16.8,9.\x*.
\p
\v 22 Ngesikhathi sohlupho lwakhe wengeza-ke ekuphambekeni emelene loJehova. Le yinkosi uAhazi.
\v 23 Ngoba wahlabela onkulunkulu beDamaseko ababemtshayile\x + 25.14.\x*, wathi: Ngoba onkulunkulu bamakhosi eSiriya bayawasiza, ngizahlabela bona ukuze bangisize\x + Jer. 44.17,18.\x*. Kodwa bona baba yimbangela yokuwa kwakhe\x + 25.8.\x*, kuye lakuIsrayeli wonke\x + 21.2.\x*.
\v 24 UAhazi waseqoqa izitsha zendlu kaNkulunkulu, waziquma iziqa izitsha zendlu kaNkulunkulu\x + 2 Kho. 16.17.\x*, wavala iminyango yendlu yeN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 29.3,7.\x*, wazenzela amalathi kuyo yonke ingonsi eJerusalema\x + 30.14.\x*.
\v 25 Lakuwo wonke umuzi ngomuzi wakoJuda wenza indawo eziphakemeyo zokutshisela abanye onkulunkulu impepha, wayithukuthelisa iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu waboyise\x + Dute. 4.25.\x*.
\p
\v 26 Ezinye-ke zezindaba zakhe lazo zonke indlela zakhe\x + 2 Kho. 16.19,20.\x*, ezokuqala lezokucina, khangela, zibhaliwe egwalweni lwamakhosi akoJuda lawakoIsrayeli\x + 1 Lan. 29.29.\x*.
\v 27 UAhazi waselala laboyise, basebemngcwabela emzini, eJerusalema; kodwa kabamlethanga emangcwabeni amakhosi\x + 21.20. 24.25.\x* akoIsrayeli\x + 21.2.\x*. UHezekhiya indodana yakhe wasesiba yinkosi esikhundleni sakhe.
